Package: com.github.tagc.semver

[Groovy] Class Version

    • com.github.tagc.semver.Version
    • All Implemented Interfaces and Traits:
      java.lang.Comparable

      @net.jcip.annotations.Immutable
class Version
extends java.lang.Object

      Represents a semantic version number for a project.

      Version objects are immutable. They can be compared based on the standard for semantic version comparisons (based on lexicographic comparison of major, minor and patch numbers).

      Authors:
      davidfallah
      Since:
      v0.1.0
